result.longName: United Projects Company For Aviation Services K.S.C.P.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: United Projects Company For Aviation Services K.S.C.P. operates as a commercial real estate development and facilities management company in Kuwait. It operates in two segments, Investments and Service Operations. The company provides airplane ground and cleaning services, as well as manages. It offers real estate management, project management and consultancy, and logistics services; and real estate development services, such as property management, sales and leasing, site development and renovation, and space design and planning. The company also provides property and facilities management services, including parking lot management, security and cleaning, check-in counters management, and engineering and custodial services; facility and equipment maintenance service comprising air conditioning, plumbing, electric, and conveyor belt services; utilities and communications infrastructure; and exterior landscaping services. United Projects Company For Aviation Services K.S.C.P. was founded in 2000 and is based in Safat, Kuwait. United Projects Company For Aviation Services K.S.C.P. is a subsidiary of Agility Public Warehousing Company K.S.C.P.
